OL,3,CAre the government's welfare reforms
OL,4,Cabout brutal cuts or job creation?
OL,6,FAccording to the OECD, in the third
OL,7,Fquarter of 2023 the UK ranked fifth in
OL,8,Fthe world, with an employment rate of
OL,9,F74.9%, well ahead of the US for
OL,10,Fexample, and behind only Iceland, the
OL,11,FNetherlands, Japan and Germany.
